OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with rain and hill snow
OL,7,Fcontinuing to spread eastwards, heavy
OL,8,Fat times. Rain clearing east
OL,9,Fovernight, replaced by showers and
OL,10,Fdrier spells. Strongest winds easing
OL,11,Fovernight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FBlustery showers feeding in
OL,14,Ffrom the west throughout the day, with
OL,15,Fsome bright spells between showers.
OL,16,FSnow over hills at first but becoming
OL,17,Fincreasingly wintry to low levels
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
