OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,6,Fand bright spells early Saturday, then
OL,7,Frain, shill snow, and very strong
OL,8,Fwinds spreading north later. Blustery
OL,9,Fshowers as winds ease through Sunday.
OL,10,FMostly dry on Monday, windier later.
